      </structure>
    </statement>
    <statement id="617.txt-4">
      <text>Ray corolla laminae abaxially white to ochroleucous or yellowish (often marked with blue to purple), adaxially mostly whitish (often blue to purplish at bases and/or apices), 20–30+ mm.</text>
